("Iron Point", "polearm", 2, 243, "None", "None", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Iron_Point.png"),
("White Tassel", "polearm", 3, 401, "CRIT Rate 23.4% (5.1%)", "Sharp\nIncreases Normal Attack DMG by 24~48%.", "/images/weapons/Weapon_White_Tassel.png"),
("Halberd", "polearm", 3, 448, "ATK 23.4% (5.1%)", "Heavy\nNormal Attacks deal an additional 160~320% DMG. Can only occur once every 10s.", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Halberd.png"),
("Black Tassel", "polearm", 3, 354, "HP 46.9% (10.2%)", "Bane of the Soft\nIncreases DMG against slimes by 40~80%.", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Black_Tassel.png"),
("Wavebreaker's Fin", "polearm", 4, 620, "ATK 13.8% (3%)", "Watatsumi Wavewalker\nFor every point of the entire party's combined maximum Energy capacity, the Elemental Burst DMG of the character equipping this weapon is increased by 0.12~0.24%. A maximum of 40~80% increased Elemental Burst DMG can be achieved this way. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Wavebreaker's_Fin.png"),
("Tamayuratei no Ohanashi", "polearm", 4, 565, "Energy Recharge 30.6% (6.7%)", "Busybody's Running Light\nIncrease ATK by 20~40% and Movement SPD by 10% for 10s when using an Elemental Skill. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Tamayuratei_no_Ohanashi.png"),
("Sacrificer's Staff", "polearm", 4, 620, "CRIT Rate 9.2% (2.0%)", "Untainted Desire\nFor 6s after an Elemental Skill hits an opponent, ATK is increased by 8~16% and Energy Recharge is increased by 6~12%. Max 3 stacks. This effect can be triggered even when the equipping character is off-field.", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Sacrificer's_Staff.png"),
("Royal Spear", "polearm", 4, 565, "ATK 27.6% (6%)", "Focus\nUpon dealing damage to an opponent, increases CRIT Rate by 8~16%. Max 5 stacks. A CRIT hit removes all existing stacks. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Royal_Spear.png"),
("Rightful Reward", "polearm", 4, 565, "HP 27.6% (6%)", "Tip of the Spear\nWhen the wielder is healed, restore 8~16 Energy. This effect can be triggered once every 10s, and can occur even when the character is not on the field. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Rightful_Reward.png"),
("Prototype Stargitter", "polearm", 4, 510, "Energy Recharge 45.9% (10.0%)", "Magic Affinity\nAfter using an Elemental Skill, increases Normal and Charged Attack DMG by 8~16% for 12s. Max 2 stacks. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Prototype_Stargitter.png"),
("Prospector's Shovel", "polearm", 4, 510, "ATK 41.3% (9%)", "Swift and Sure\nElectro-Charged DMG is increased by 48~96%, and Lunar-Charged DMG is increased by 12~24%. Moonsign: Ascendant Gleam: Lunar-Charged DMG is increased by an additional 12~24%. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Prospector's_Shovel.png"),
("Prospector's Drill", "polearm", 4, 565, "ATK 27.6% (6%)", "Masons' Ditty\nWhen the wielder is healed or heals others, they will gain a Unity's Symbol that lasts 30s, up to a maximum of 3 Symbols. When using their Elemental Skill or Burst, all Symbols will be consumed and the Struggle effect will be granted for 10s. For each Symbol consumed, gain 3~7% ATK and 7~13% All Elemental DMG Bonus. The Struggle effect can be triggered once every 15s, and Symbols can be gained even when the character is not on the field. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Prospector's_Drill.png"),
("Mountain Bracing Bolt", "polearm", 4, 565, "Energy Recharge 30.6% (6.7%)", "Hope Beyond the Peaks\nDecreases Climbing Stamina Consumption by 15% and increases Elemental Skill DMG by 12~24%. Also, after other nearby party members use Elemental Skills, the equipping character's Elemental Skill DMG will also increase by 12~24% for 8s. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Mountain_Bracing_Bolt.png"),
("Moonpiercer", "polearm", 4, 565, "Elemental Mastery 110 (24)", "Stillwood Moonshadow\nAfter triggering Burning, Quicken, Aggravate, Spread, Bloom, Hyperbloom, or Burgeon, a Leaf of Revival will be created around the character for a maximum of 10s. When picked up, the Leaf will grant the character 16~32% ATK for 12s. Only 1 Leaf can be generated this way every 20s. This effect can still be triggered if the character is not on the field. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Moonpiercer.png"),
("Missive Windspear", "polearm", 4, 510, "ATK 41.3% (9%)", "The Wind Unattained\nWithin 10s after an Elemental Reaction is triggered, ATK is increased by 12~24% and Elemental Mastery is increased by 48~96. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Missive_Windspear.png"),
("Lithic Spear", "polearm", 4, 565, "ATK 27.6% (6%)", "Lithic Axiom: Unity\nFor every character in the party who hails from Liyue, the character who equips this weapon gains 7~11% ATK increase and a 3~7% CRIT Rate increase. This effect stacks up to 4 times. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Lithic_Spear.png"),
("Kitain Cross Spear", "polearm", 4, 565, "Elemental Mastery 110 (24)", "Samurai Conduct\nIncreases Elemental Skill DMG by 6~12%. After Elemental Skill hits an opponent, the character loses 3 Energy but regenerates 3~5 Energy every 2s for the next 6s. This effect can occur once every 10s. Can be triggered even when the character is not on the field. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Kitain_Cross_Spear.png"),
("Footprint of the Rainbow", "polearm", 4, 510, "DEF 51.7% (11.3%)", "Pact of Flowing Springs\nUsing an Elemental Skill increases DEF by 16~32% for 15s. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Footprint_of_the_Rainbow.png"),
("Favonius Lance", "polearm", 4, 565, "Energy Recharge 30.6% (6.7%)", "Windfall\nCRIT Hits have a 60~100% chance to generate a small amount of Elemental Particles, which will regenerate 6 Energy for the character. Can only occur once every 12~6s. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Favonius_Lance.png"),
("Dragonspine Spear", "polearm", 4, 454, "Physical DMG Bonus 69.0% (15%)", "Frost Burial\nHitting an opponent with Normal and Charged Attacks has a 60~100% chance of forming and dropping an Everfrost Icicle above them, dealing 80~140% AoE ATK DMG. Opponents affected by Cryo are dealt 200~360% ATK DMG instead by the icicle. Can only occur once every 10s. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Dragonspine_Spear.png"),
("Dragon's Bane", "polearm", 4, 454, "Elemental Mastery 221 (48)", "Bane of Flame and Water\nIncreases DMG against opponents affected by Hydro or Pyro by 20~36%. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Dragon's_Bane.png"),
("Dialogues of the Desert Sages", "polearm", 4, 510, "HP 41.3% (9%)", "Principle of Equilibrium\nWhen the wielder performs healing, restore 8~16 Energy. This effect can be triggered once every 10s and can occur even when the character is not on the field. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Dialogues_of_the_Desert_Sages.png"),
("Deathmatch", "polearm", 4, 454, "CRIT Rate 36.8% (8%)", "Gladiator\nIf there are at least 2 opponents nearby, ATK is increased by 16~32% and DEF is increased by 16~32%. If there are fewer than 2 opponents nearby, ATK is increased by 24~48%. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Deathmatch.png"),
("Crescent Pike", "polearm", 4, 565, "Physical DMG Bonus 34.5% (7.5%)", "Infusion Needle\nAfter picking up an Elemental Orb/Particle, Normal and Charged Attacks deal an additional 20~40% ATK as DMG for 5s. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Crescent_Pike.png"),
("Blackcliff Pole", "polearm", 4, 510, "CRIT DMG 55.1% (12%)", "Press the Advantage\nAfter defeating an opponent, ATK is increased by 12~24% for 30s. This effect has a maximum of 3 stacks, and the duration of each stack is independent of the others. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Blackcliff_Pole.png"),
("Ballad of the Fjords", "polearm", 4, 510, "CRIT Rate 27.6% (6%)", "Tales of the Tundra\nWhen there are at least 3 different Elemental Types in your party, Elemental Mastery will be increased by 120~240. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Ballad_of_the_Fjords.png"),
("The Catch", "polearm", 4, 510, "Energy Recharge 45.9% (10.0%)", "Shanty\nIncreases Elemental Burst DMG by 16~32% and Elemental Burst CRIT Rate by 6~12%. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_The_Catch.png"),
("Vortex Vanquisher", "polearm", 5, 608, "ATK 49.6% (10.8%)", "Golden Majesty\nIncreases Shield Strength by 20~40%. Scoring hits on opponents increases ATK by 4~8% for 8s. Max 5 stacks. Can only occur once every 0.3s. While protected by a shield, this ATK increase effect is increased by 100%. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Vortex_Vanquisher.png"),
("Symphonist of Scents", "polearm", 5, 608, "CRIT DMG 66.2% (14.4%)", 'Seasoned Symphony\nATK is increased by 12~24%. When the equipping character is off-field, ATK is increased by an additional 12~24%. After initiating healing, the equipping character and the character(s) they have healed will obtain the "Sweet Echoes" effect, increasing their ATK by 32~64% for 3s. This effect can be triggered even if the equipping character is off-field. ', "/images/weapons/Weapon_Symphonist_of_Scents.png"),
("Staff of the Scarlet Sands", "polearm", 5, 542, "CRIT Rate 44.1% (9.6%)", "Heat Haze at Horizon's End\nThe equipping character gains 52~104% of their Elemental Mastery as bonus ATK. When an Elemental Skill hits opponents, the Dream of the Scarlet Sands effect will be gained for 10s: The equipping character will gain 28~56% of their Elemental Mastery as bonus ATK. Max 3 stacks. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Staff_of_the_Scarlet_Sands.png"),
("Staff of Homa", "polearm", 5, 608, "CRIT DMG 66.2% (14.4%)", "Reckless Cinnabar\nHP increased by 20~40%. Additionally, provides an ATK Bonus based on 0.8~1.6% of the wielder's Max HP. When the wielder's HP is less than 50%, this ATK bonus is increased by an additional 1~1.8% of Max HP. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Staff_of_Homa.png"),
("Skyward Spine", "polearm", 5, 674, "Energy Recharge 36.8% (8%)", "Black Wing\nIncreases CRIT Rate by 8~16% and increases Normal ATK SPD by 12%. Additionally, Normal and Charged Attacks hits on opponents have a 50% chance to trigger a vacuum blade that deals 40~100% of ATK as DMG in a small AoE. This effect can occur no more than once every 2s. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Skyward_Spine.png"),
("Primordial Jade Winged-Spear", "polearm", 5, 674, "CRIT Rate 22.1% (4.8%)", "Eagle Spear of Justice\nOn hit, increases ATK by 3.2~6.0% for 6s. Max 7 stacks. This effect can only occur once every 0.3s. While in possession of the maximum possible stacks, DMG dealt is increased by 12~24%. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Primordial_Jade_Winged-Spear.png"),
("Lumidouce Elegy", "polearm", 5, 608, "CRIT Rate 33.1% (7.2%)", "Bright Dawn Overture\nATK increased by 15~31%. After the equipping character triggers Burning on an opponent or deals Dendro DMG to Burning opponents, the DMG dealt is increased by 18~38%. This effect lasts for 8s, max 2 stacks. When 2 stacks are reached or when the duration is refreshed at 2 stacks, restore 12~16 Energy. Energy can be restored this way once every 12s. The 2 aforementioned effects can be triggered even when the character is off-field. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Lumidouce_Elegy.png"),
("Fractured Halo", "polearm", 5, 608, "CRIT DMG 66.2% (14.4%)", "Purifying Crown\nAfter an Elemental Skill or Elemental Burst is used, ATK is increased by 24~48% for 20s. If the equipping character creates a Shield while this effect is active, they will gain the Electrifying Edict effect for 20s: All nearby party members deal 40~80% more Lunar-Charged DMG. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Fractured_Halo.png"),
("Engulfing Lightning", "polearm", 5, 608, "Energy Recharge 55.1% (12%)", "Timeless Dream: Eternal Stove\nATK increased by 28~56% of Energy Recharge over the base 100%. You can gain a maximum bonus of 80~120% ATK. Gain 30~50% Energy Recharge for 12s after using an Elemental Burst. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Engulfing_Lightning.png"),
("Crimson Moon's Semblance", "polearm", 5, 674, "CRIT Rate 22.1% (4.8%)", "Ashen Sun's Shadow\nGrants a Bond of Life equal to 25% of Max HP when a Charged Attack hits an opponent. This effect can be triggered up to once every 14s. In addition, when the equipping character has a Bond of Life, they gain a 12~28% DMG Bonus; if the value of the Bond of Life is greater than or equal to 30% of Max HP, then gain an additional 24~56% DMG. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Crimson_Moon's_Semblance.png"),
("Calamity Queller", "polearm", 5, 741, "ATK 16.5% (3.6%)", "Extinguishing Precept\nGain 12~24% All Elemental DMG Bonus. Obtain Consummation for 20s after using an Elemental Skill, causing ATK to increase by 3.2~6.4% per second. This ATK increase has a maximum of 6 stacks. When the character equipped with this weapon is not on the field, Consummation's ATK increase is doubled. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Calamity_Queller.png"),
("Bloodsoaked Ruins", "polearm", 5, 674, "CRIT RATE 22.1% (4.8%)", "Mournful Tribute\nFor 3.5s after using an Elemental Burst, the equipping character's Lunar-Charged DMG dealt to opponents is increased by 36~84%. Additionally, after triggering a Lunar-Charged reaction, the equipping character will gain Requiem of Ruin: CRIT DMG is increased by 28~56% for 6s. They will also regain 12~16 Elemental Energy. Elemental Energy can be restored this way once every 14s. ", "/images/weapons/Weapon_Bloodsoaked_Ruins.png")



